WEBVTT

00:01:27.998 --> 00:01:32.117
First, never before

00:01:32.141 --> 00:01:38.727
we will inflict on the economy
consciously so much pain

00:01:38.751 --> 00:01:41.679
to fight a virus and save lives.

00:01:42.331 --> 00:01:45.627
We are asking businesses not to produce

00:01:45.651 --> 00:01:48.601
and consumers not to go out and consume.

00:01:48.625 --> 00:01:53.410
At the Fund, we labeled this
"the Great Lockdown."

00:01:54.673 --> 00:01:56.180
Second,

00:01:56.204 --> 00:01:59.048
never before

00:01:59.072 --> 00:02:05.820
there would be such
a rapid change of fortunes